OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F163A1777299067
OL,1,Wj5hw1~{4k7juhw1{$             G2/2
OL,2,W+.-'"-$/*%*%*%/"-$/*%Q,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GUK long range forecast
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Tue 12 May to Tue 26 May
OL,6,FLow pressure systems are likely to
OL,7,Fdominate across the UK at the start of
OL,8,Fthis period. This means showers or
OL,9,Flonger spells of rain are likely at
OL,10,Ftimes, heavy in places, with a risk of
OL,11,Fstrong winds. There will, however, be
OL,12,Fsome dry and warm interludes, although
OL,13,Ftemperatures are likely to be close to
OL,14,Fnormal. Later in the month, more
OL,15,Fsettled and drier conditions may begin
OL,16,Fto develop, with temperatures perhaps
OL,17,Frising slightly above normal.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
